Roy F. Coppedge III, MBA

Age : 69Public asset : 113,231 USDLinked companies :  Saga Communications, Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. Roy F. Coppedge is on the Board of Directors at Saga Communications, Inc. and Wireless Broadcasting Systems of America, Inc. Mr. Coppedge was previously employed as Senior Advisor by BV Investment Partners LLC and Vice President by BankBoston, NA.He received his undergraduate degree from Harvard College and an MBA from Harvard University.



